[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 2.0,
    "text": "Look, all I know is the food looked iffy, all right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.0,
    "endTime": 4.0,
    "text": "And I'm not the only one who thinks that, I'm sure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.0,
    "endTime": 5.0,
    "text": "Hey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.0,
    "endTime": 9.0,
    "text": "So I'm just checking to make sure you're gonna take the main course up a notch."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.0,
    "endTime": 12.0,
    "text": "Is there anything on this menu that is not swimming in gravy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.0,
    "endTime": 14.0,
    "text": "Hang on, I'll go ask the chef."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.0,
    "endTime": 15.0,
    "text": "It's a simple question."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.0,
    "endTime": 18.0,
    "text": "Is there or is there not anything edible on this menu?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.0,
    "endTime": 19.0,
    "text": "Go!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.0,
    "endTime": 23.0,
    "text": "Hey, I didn't ask him about dessert yet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.0,
    "endTime": 26.0,
    "text": "Hey, pal, what's your policy on making special orders?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.0,
    "endTime": 28.0,
    "text": "All right, buster, that's it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.0,
    "endTime": 29.0,
    "text": "You want a special order?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.0,
    "endTime": 30.0,
    "text": "Then you make it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 30.0,
    "text": "I quit!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.0,
    "endTime": 33.0,
    "text": "You know, I try and I try."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.0,
    "endTime": 34.0,
    "text": "There's just no respect for anyone with vision."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.0,
    "endTime": 37.0,
    "text": "That's it, there's just nothing I can do about it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.0,
    "endTime": 38.0,
    "text": "Oh, wait a second, please don't go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.0,
    "endTime": 46.0,
    "text": "Four combos, extra bacon on the side, two chili cheese samplers, a basket of liver and onion rings, a catch of the day, and a steak cut in the shape of a trout."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.0,
    "endTime": 48.0,
    "text": "You got all that, honey?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.0,
    "endTime": 52.0,
    "text": "Three oinkers wearing pants, plate of hot air, basket of grandma's breakfast, and change the bowl to a gill."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.0,
    "endTime": 52.0,
    "text": "Got it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.0,
    "endTime": 54.0,
    "text": "What's going on?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.0,
    "endTime": 55.0,
    "text": "There's no time to explain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.0,
    "endTime": 55.0,
    "text": "We gotta get out of here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.0,
    "endTime": 59.0,
    "text": "What is he doing in there?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.0,
    "endTime": 63.0,
    "text": "Come on!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.0,
    "endTime": 64.0,
    "text": "In a minute, I'm still hungry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.0,
    "endTime": 66.0,
    "text": "Oh, who's called?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.0,
    "endTime": 67.0,
    "text": "Okay, I'll make it simple for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.0,
    "endTime": 69.0,
    "text": "I'll have a spinach omelet with wheat toast."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.0,
    "endTime": 70.0,
    "text": "You got it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.0,
    "endTime": 70.0,
    "text": "Can do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.0,
    "endTime": 72.0,
    "text": "What's taking so long?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.0,
    "endTime": 74.0,
    "text": "Becka!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.0,
    "endTime": 75.0,
    "text": "Kronk, what are you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.0,
    "endTime": 76.0,
    "text": "Kinda busy here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.0,
    "endTime": 78.0,
    "text": "Why am I not surprised?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.0,
    "endTime": 79.0,
    "text": "Your order's up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.0,
    "endTime": 80.0,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.0,
    "endTime": 81.0,
    "text": "Oh, well."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.0,
    "endTime": 83.0,
    "text": "While you're at it, make me the special."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.0,
    "endTime": 84.0,
    "text": "And hold the gravy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.0,
    "endTime": 85.0,
    "text": "Check."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.0,
    "endTime": 86.0,
    "text": "Pick up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.0,
    "endTime": 86.0,
    "text": "You know what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.0,
    "endTime": 88.0,
    "text": "On second thought, make my omelet a meat pie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.0,
    "endTime": 89.0,
    "text": "Meat pie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.0,
    "endTime": 89.0,
    "text": "Check."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.0,
    "endTime": 90.0,
    "text": "Kronk!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.0,
    "endTime": 93.0,
    "text": "Can I order the potatoes as a side dish?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.0,
    "endTime": 94.0,
    "text": "I'll have to charge you full price."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.0,
    "endTime": 97.0,
    "text": "Hey, how about a side of potatoes, my buddy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.0,
    "endTime": 98.0,
    "text": "You got it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.0,
    "endTime": 99.0,
    "text": "You want cheese on those potatoes?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.0,
    "endTime": 99.0,
    "text": "Thank you, Kronk."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.0,
    "endTime": 100.0,
    "text": "Cheddar will be fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.0,
    "endTime": 101.0,
    "text": "Cheddar spuds coming up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.0,
    "endTime": 102.0,
    "text": "Spuds, yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.0,
    "endTime": 102.0,
    "text": "Cheese, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.0,
    "endTime": 103.0,
    "text": "Hold the cheese."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.0,
    "endTime": 104.0,
    "text": "No, I want the cheese."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.0,
    "endTime": 104.0,
    "text": "Cheese it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.0,
    "endTime": 105.0,
    "text": "Cheese me no likey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.0,
    "endTime": 106.0,
    "text": "Cheese out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.0,
    "endTime": 106.0,
    "text": "Cheese in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.0,
    "endTime": 107.0,
    "text": "Oh, come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.0,
    "endTime": 107.0,
    "text": "Make up your mind."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 108.0,
    "text": "Okay, okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 110.0,
    "text": "On second thought, make my potatoes a salad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.0,
    "endTime": 116.0,
    "text": "Oh, wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.0,
    "endTime": 127.0,
    "text": "Excuse me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.0,
    "endTime": 128.0,
    "text": "You see that over there?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.0,
    "endTime": 129.0,
    "text": "There's a woman with a thing on her piece of cake."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.0,
    "endTime": 131.0,
    "text": "No problem, hon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.0,
    "endTime": 132.0,
    "text": "We do that all the time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.0,
    "endTime": 138.0,
    "text": "One, two, three, four!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.0,
    "endTime": 140.0,
    "text": "Happy, happy birthday, from all of us to you!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.0,
    "endTime": 143.0,
    "text": "Wish it was our birthday, so we could party, too!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.0,
